// Title: New IP Address Sign-in
// Description: Detects successful sign-ins from IP addresses rarely used by the account
// Data Source: SigninLogs
// MITRE ATT&CK:
//   Tactic: TA0001 - Initial Access
//   Technique: T1078 - Valid Accounts
// Severity: Medium
// References:
// - https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1078/

SigninLogs
| where ResultType == 0
| summarize LoginCount = count() by UserPrincipalName, IPAddress
| where LoginCount < 3
| sort by LoginCount
